## ✍️ Style Comparison

To compare writing styles:
- Upload a `.txt` file with your writing sample
- The app will show how closely the new text matches your tone and structure

---

## 🔐 Optional: AI Detection API

You can paste an API key (e.g., GPTZero) into the sidebar. It's never saved.

